 nter invites you to join the Resilience &amp\; Resource Collective\, a st
 udent-led group focused on housing\, finances\, and mental health. Listen
 ing counts. No shame. No fixing. Just collective wisdom and practical res
 ources.Across three sessions\, we'll demystify housing systems\, share co
 llege funding strategies\, and reflect on what helped us get through the 
