 s of produce from OFB and add in backstock of non-perishable items to dis
 tribute to community members. Free Food Market is a one-off event that is
  scheduled around our campus delivery schedule from the OFB. This event i
 s open to all.<br />No ID is needed to attend\, we only ask how many are 
 in their household. We ask that participants bring their own bag or box t
 o transport the food.<br />â€”<br />Event Details: <a href="https://hub.p
