SUMMARY:Sylvania Free Food Market
DESCRIPTION:Free Food Markets are community events that center fresh prod
 uce provided by the Oregon Food Bank. We get large orders of produce from
  OFB and add in backstock of non-perishable items to distribute to commun
 ity members. Free Food Market is a one-off event that is scheduled around
  our campus delivery schedule from the OFB. This event is open to all.No 
 ID is needed to attend\, we only ask how many are in their household. We 
 ask that participants bring their own bag or box to transport the food.â€
